# Mastermind Monorepo

## Architecture

```
mastermind/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/            → Next.js 15 + shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS v4       :3000
│   ├── admin/          → Next.js 15 + shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS v4       :3002
│   ├── docs/           → Mintlify documentation                         :3003
│   ├── react-native/   → Expo + Expo Router + NativeWind
│   ├── remotion/       → Remotion video generation                    :3004
│   └── server/         → Fastify + Swagger API server                   :3001
├── packages/
│   ├── db/             → Drizzle ORM + Neon PostgreSQL (shared schema)
│   ├── wallet/         → EVM wallet generation & HD derivation (viem)
│   ├── eslint-config/  → Shared ESLint configs
│   └── typescript-config/ → Shared TypeScript configs
```

## Package Relationships

- `apps/web`, `apps/admin`, and `apps/server` depend on `@repo/db`
- All apps use `@repo/eslint-config` and `@repo/typescript-config`
- Each Next.js app has its own independent shadcn/ui install

## Key Commands

- `pnpm dev` — start all apps
- `pnpm dev:web` / `pnpm dev:admin` / `pnpm dev:server` — start individual apps
- `pnpm db:push` — push schema to database
- `pnpm db:generate` — generate migrations
- `pnpm db:studio` — open Drizzle Studio

## Package Manager

This project uses **pnpm 10** with workspaces. Always use `pnpm` (never npm or yarn).
